# BP Fundamental Analysis with AI Agents

## Project Overview
This project develops an AI-assisted system to automate fundamental equity analysis
using BP plc as a case study. The analysis evaluates BP’s financial performance,
risk profile, and intrinsic value based on data from 2020 to 2024.

## Data Source
- Yahoo Finance
- Alpha Vantage
- BP Annual Reports

## Main Functions
- Financial data collection (Income Statement, Balance Sheet, Cash Flow)
- Data cleaning and validation
- Financial ratio analysis
- Free Cash Flow (FCF) calculation
- Discounted Cash Flow (DCF) valuation
- Dividend Discount Model (DDM) valuation
- Relative valuation (Multiples)

